reviewText:
One installment of a very long series - this episode is a visit to Austria.
Excellent performances and excellent production values.
I understood this would be a DVD but it was a  VHS which I cannot play.

Queen Mary II arrived in original wrapper. 1) Wrong DVD. Ordered European Church Organs.  2) Paper from DVD disintegrated into my SONY DVD player and ruined it!!

The shipper said: "We tried it, it was fine".

Nada, it was in the Original Wrapper!!!  :(
